Package: pantheia_model
Title: PANTHEIA-SIRI Prognostic Model: Calculator and Reproducible Tables
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Alberto", "Carmona-Bayonas", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "carmonab@um.es")
Description: Fitted PANTHEIA-SIRI prognostic models (3-level tumour-burden
    coding) for overall survival in metastatic pancreatic ductal adenocarcinoma,
    an interactive Shiny calculator, and a one-command script that reproduces
    the coefficient table (Table 2) and the discrimination/calibration table
    (Table 3) of the external-validation paper from de-identified analysis
    datasets.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
    ggplot2,
    scales,
    shiny,
    splines,
    survival
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
